narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: critical analysis and love in analysis
So much about race and sexuality and their intersections.
I learned how to write and think critically about gender and sexuality and how these concepts play it outside of the US. I saw myself represented in the classroom!

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: This course was amazing - the themes were engaging and the readings were excellent. My only feedback is that I wish the readings were posted online earlier.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Absolutely. It will challenge you, build your curiosity, and really teach you.
